- Each player has 1 butterfly, 5 sparrows
X Each piece can be placed, cannot move
X Piece cannot be placed on another piece
- Butterfly must be placed by 4th turn, if not, only legal move is butterfly
X Players can only place 1 Butterfly
- Game can last no more than 6 turns
- Game can end if butterfly is surrounded before 6th turn
- Test Blue wins
- Test Red wins
X Pieces must be placed adjacent to at least one other piece, regardless of owner
- Game ends in draw if no winner after 6 moves
- Any illegal move: player loses, HantoException with appropriate message thrown
- No moves made after Game Over. Else, HantoException thrown